64.6	Vilayanur_S._Ramachandran	Vilayanur S. Ramachandran	Vilayanur Subramanian Ramachandran (Tamil: , born 1951) is a neuroscientist known for his work in the fields of behavioral neurology and visual psychophysics. He is the Director of the Center for Brain and Cognition, and is currently a Professor in the Department of Psychology and the Neurosciences Graduate Program at the University of California, San Diego.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a5/Vilayanur_S_Ramachandran_2011_Shankbone.JPG/220px-Vilayanur_S_Ramachandran_2011_Shankbone.JPG
